snippet.title: Star Wars Battlefront II: Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Fight in legendary battles across all three eras in Star Wars™ Battlefront™ II. 

Subscribe for upcoming Star Wars Battlefront II video’s: http://bit.ly/2oDLwKI 

Star Wars Battlefront II will be available on PlayStation 4, Xbox One, and PC

Release Date: November 17, 2017

See more from EA Play 2017: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLLy6qvPKpdlV3OAw00EuZMoYPz4pYuwuN
